# Data Model Impact Sweep

When entities/attributes/relations/cardinalities change:

- Perform an explicit dependent-layer impact sweep.
- Update models, schema/contracts, routers/services, frontend API consumers, and docs as needed.
- Treat seed updates as mandatory and include seed-impact review in the same change set.
